high_descs: Turn left and walk forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Pick up the sponge from off the counter.
Turn around and walk over to the kitchen island.
Put the sponge in the glass bowl that is on the kitchen island.
Pick up the glass bowl with the sponge in it.
Walk over to where the toaster is on the counter and look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the rightmost upper cabinet in front of you and put the bowl with the sponge in it inside, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass bowl with a sponge in it a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn to the left, and the left again to face the sink.
Pick up the sponge from the left side, behind the sink.
Take the sponge and turn around to the island.
Place the sponge in the bowl on the front left side of the island.
Pick up the bowl from the front left side of the island.
Take the bowl and turn to the left, then the right to go back to the toaster. Look up above the toaster.
Open the cabinet and place the bowl and sponge inside. Shut the cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Move a bowl and sponge to the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left move forward then face the sink on your left
Pick up the sponge from the sink
Turn right forward facing the island
Put the sponge in the bowl on the island
Pick up the bowl with sponge
Turn left move forward then turn right head to the cabinet above the counter on your left
Put the bowl with sponge in the last cabinet on your left
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl with sponge in the cabinet
